<taxonomicName id="01BD3517935C8C15453E37F3776A096A" genus="D." lsidName="D. shandongense" pageId="5" pageNumber="72" rank="species" species="shandongense">D. shandongense</taxonomicName>
by the existence of obvious central column.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
